HEADWORD: Inconcoction
<hw>In`con*coc"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The state of
being undigested; unripeness; immaturity.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Bacon.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
